\f1\u-10179?\u-9012?\f2  \f0 Overview\par
\par
Permaculture Design Intelligence Platform is a web-based, AI-assisted geospatial application designed for land regeneration, water management, and sustainable agricultural planning across India.\par
\par
This platform provides professional tools to understand:\par
\par
Terrain\par
\par
Hydrology\par
\par
Sun Path\par
\par
Slope & Aspect\par
\par
Contours\par
\par
Soil & Vegetation\par
\par
Zone Planning\par
\par
Crop Suitability\par
\par
It transforms raw geography into actionable design intelligence, suitable for:\par
\par
Farmers\par
\par
Land Developers\par
\par
Environmental Consultants\par
\par
NGOs\par
\par
Ecologists\par
\par
Sustainability Teams\par
\par
Government Agencies\par
\par
Built using only open-source data and zero-cost cloud infrastructure, the system is deployable on GitHub Pages (frontend) and Render.com (backend).\par
\par
